"performance and wide range of functionality. For detailed derivations of "
"this model please refer to [\"A Note on Deriving the Pareto/NBD Model and"
" Related "
"Expressions.\"](https://www.brucehardie.com/notes/009/pareto_nbd_derivations_2005-11-05.pdf)"
